cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing tasks and recurrent neural networks. It could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves analyzing and interpreting the behavior of neural networks. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it deals with recurrent neural networks, and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it involves detecting saliency patterns in decision making.
